<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="426">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-kun-62" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-kun-62" class="zg-link" title="刘坤">刘坤</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ye-xin-jia-64" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ye-xin-jia-64" class="zg-link" title="野心家">野心家</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gan-yu-tong-85" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gan-yu-tong-85" class="zg-link" title="BellaX">BellaX</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
